---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Security (Anti-Gravity) - LaventeCare">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 text-center md:text-left">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start space-x-3 mb-6">
        <div class="h-px bg-active w-12"></div>
        <span class="text-active font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm font-display">Anti-Gravity</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-8 font-display tracking-tight">Vertrouwen door Diepgang</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 font-ui leading-relaxed">
        In een wereld vol cyberdreigingen is "goed genoeg" niet meer voldoende. Wij hanteren een militaire standaard voor uw data-integriteit en veiligheid, gebaseerd op onze 5 onbreekbare wetten.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- The 5 Laws -->
    <div class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-12 text-center md:text-left font-display">De 5 Wetten van Anti-Gravity</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        
        <!-- Law 1 -->
        <div class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">1. Input is Toxic</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            Wij vertrouwen niets. Elke input, elke parameter en elke header wordt beschouwd als vijandig totdat het tegendeel is bewezen via strikte validatie.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Strict Marshaling & Validation
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Law 2 -->
        <div class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">🤫</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">2. Silence is Golden</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            Wij lekken nooit interne informatie. Foutmeldingen zijn generiek voor de buitenwereld, maar kristalhelder in onze beveiligde audit logs.
          </p>
           <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            No Stack Traces Leaked
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Law 3 -->
        <div class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">🏰</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">3. Database Fortress</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            SQL Injection is wiskundig onmogelijk gemaakt. Uw data is geïsoleerd op query-niveau, alsof elke klant zijn eigen kluis heeft.
          </p>
           <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Type-Safe SQL & Tenant Isolation
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Law 4 -->
        <div class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">4. Race Conditions are Fatal</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            In een snelle omgeving telt elke milliseconde. Wij beschermen de staat van uw applicatie rigoureus tegen conflicten, zelfs onder zware belasting.
          </p>
           <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Stateless Handlers & Mutexes
          </div>
        </div>

         <!-- Law 5 -->
        <div class="clinical-glass p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-active/50 transition-colors group">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">📦</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">5. Dependency Paranoia</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 font-ui">
            Wij bouwen op bewezen technologie, niet op de "flavor of the month". Minimale afhankelijkheden betekenen maximale stabiliteit en veiligheid.
          </p>
           <div class="text-xs text-white/40 font-mono bg-black/20 p-2 rounded">
            Standard Library First
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Database Fortress & Compliance Detail -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-7 clinical-glass p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center font-display">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-active mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"></path></svg>
          Technical Deep Dive: <span class="text-active">RLS</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed font-ui">
          Onze <strong>PostgreSQL</strong> database gebruikt <span class="text-white font-bold">Row Level Security (RLS)</span>. Dit betekent dat de database <span class="text-active italic">*zelf*</span> handhaaft wie welke data mag zien. Zelfs als de applicatielogic zou falen (wat we voorkomen via Wet #1), weigert de database simpelweg data te tonen aan de verkeerde gebruiker.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start text-white/80 font-ui">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <span>Diepe verdedigingslinie (<span class="text-white font-medium">Defense in Depth</span>)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start text-white/80 font-ui">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <span>Automatische <span class="text-white font-medium">encryptie</span> van gevoelige velden</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 clinical-glass p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center font-display">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-active mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
          Audit Logs & Compliance
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          Compliance is geen vinkje, het is een mindset. Elke kritieke actie in het systeem laat een onuitwisbaar spoor achter.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
                <span class="text-white/60 text-sm">Login Attempt</span>
                <span class="text-active text-xs font-mono">2026-01-29 19:42:01 UTC</span>
            </div>
             <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
                <span class="text-white/60 text-sm">Policy Change</span>
                <span class="text-active text-xs font-mono">2026-01-29 19:45:12 UTC</span>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
